en-US.title: Neighborcare Health
en-US.description: Neighborcare Health is a healthcare center that provides various health-related services such as medical, pregnancy, children, dental, mental health and social work, school-based, homeless and housing, and after hours care. It promotes cultural sensitivity and community health, showcasing patient success stories and aspiring to social justice and excellence.

address: 10521 Meridian Ave N, Seattle, WA 98133, USA
